ra WordPress blocks JS-files was such a good idea?</p>\n<p>Update: additionally the change also introduces nonces (random password-like strings as hidden elements in the form) which can spell serious trouble when using page caching plugins.</p>\n<div class=\'yarpp yarpp-related yarpp-related-rss yarpp-template-list\'>\n<!-- YARPP List -->\n<p>Possibly related twitterless twaddle:<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.futtta.be/2016/12/07/wordpress-4-7-custom-background-image-bug-workaround/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"WordPress 4.7 custom background image bug &#038; workaround\">WordPress 4.7 custom background image bug &#038; workaround </a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.futtta.be/2018/11/17/warning-divi-purging-autoptimizes-cache/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Warning: Divi purging Autoptimize&#8217;s cache!\">Warning: Divi purging Autoptimize&#8217;s cache! </a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.futtta.be/2021/03/15/contact-form-7-alternatives/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Contact Form 7 alternatives\">Contact Form 7 alternatives </a></li>\n</ul></p>\n</div>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/futtta_autoptimize/~4/FoNmwNGHNBE\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:107:\"https://blog.futtta.be/2021/02/25/contact-form-7-update-breaks-autoptimize-js-optimization-workaround/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"9\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:102:\"https://blog.futtta.be/2021/02/25/contact-form-7-update-bre